{"tid":2241619,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］是咁的 我搞左個時裝品牌","createTime":"2020-10-13T12:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T14:01:29.000Z","uid":127511,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69da05091947b002dcb55a1c33a89485926ebbf9","tid":2241619,"uid":127511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"經典回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我同一個朋友就創立咗一個牌子 Bees<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靈感就係來自一首詩 《蜂》<br />\n詩中有一句 採得百花成蜜後 為誰辛苦為誰甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好比現今社會 人類就好似工具一樣 做緊一啲對自己無意義嘅工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成就緊其他人 然後一生就咁虛耗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n古人一千幾年前嘅反省 估唔到 一千幾百年過去 好似仍然存在緊呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁目前就整咗第一個系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ponV5YH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FponV5YH.jpg&h=6d69c78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qce11gq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQce11gq.jpg&h=da5f3302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSLTSpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSLTSpN.jpg&h=a613c8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g23aUC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg23aUC8.jpg&h=c76c5e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就喺呢度順便講下我地遇過嘅挫折啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我地兩個一個住北區 一個住九龍西 真好難成日見面去傾 之後我地膽粗粗租左個臨時辦公室開始左我地嘅夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n設計 布料 同廠家磋商 到成品 擺貨地方 全部都要我地去面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到呢度諗住已經踏入大直路 只能說少年 太年輕鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地同第一個廠商整左數十件成品出來 結果不如理想 要報銷 真係深受打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地依然無放棄到 繼續去聯絡第二個廠家 結果又遇到困難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為對方要求我地一個款式最少要幾百件 佢地先會起貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對於兩個剛剛撞板嘅傻仔 再要我地投放更多資金 真係好大風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我地掙扎左好耐 覺得值得博多一次 就決定去馬 結果就真係出左一批我地滿意嘅成品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/685Qasd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F685Qasd.jpg&h=cdc0f877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46pJvf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46pJvf8.jpg&h=d2f3c823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pG1LJA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpG1LJA9.jpg&h=f602a956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32SZN2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32SZN2R.jpg&h=a36fab73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 我地覺得賣出街 首先要過到我地自己 所以第一批我地選擇報銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n件衫設計上都有啲特點 而且呢兩個月黎都發生左好多故事 如果有興趣再問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n價錢合理 質料唔錯 希望大家支持下本地品牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後希望大家可以FOLLOW IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bees_official2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbees_official2018%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=1eb1fb1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/bees_official2018/</a><br />\n網站:<a href=\"https://beesfashionhk.wixsite.com/mysite-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeesfashionhk.wixsite.com%2Fmysite-1&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=7feeb0d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://beesfashionhk.wixsite.com/mysite-1</a>"},{"pid":"2db1304cfcc74d27e1c5cd6847f0110e6f225d02","tid":2241619,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題,點解咁多人屌"}]}